      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Architecture -->
    <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 hover:bg-white/10 transition">
      <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
        <div>
          <div class="text-sm text-zinc-400">Architecture</div>
          <div class="mt-1 text-lg font-semibold">Code that scales</div>
        </div>
        <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-2 py-1 text-xs text-zinc-300">Core</span>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-xs text-zinc-300">
        <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-2 py-1">MVC</span>
        <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-2 py-1">SOLID</span>
        <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-2 py-1">OOP</span>
        <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-2 py-1">Clean Architecture</span>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-zinc-400">
        Structure first: predictable layers, maintainability, and testability.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Algorithms -->
    <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 hover:bg-white/10 transition">
      <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
        <div>
          <div class="text-sm text-zinc-400">CS fundamentals</div>
          <div class="mt-1 text-lg font-semibold">Thinking in complexity</div>
        </div>
        <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-2 py-1 text-xs text-zinc-300">Core</span>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-xs text-zinc-300">
        <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-2 py-1">Algorithms & Data Structures</span>
        <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-2 py-1">Time/Space complexity</span>
        <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-2 py-1">Competitive-style solving</span>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-zinc-400">
